creator: Noel E. Sainsbury
description:
LibriVox recording of Dorothy Dixon and the Mystery Plane by Noel E. Sainsbury.

Read in English by Susan Morin

Young peoples book of adventure in aviation with young women in the lead rolls. This is in the earlier days of aviation. - Summary by Susan Morin

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
